description: Space Race Trivia is a fun way to test your knowledge of the space race and beyond! Simply install the skill, say "Alexa, Start Space Race Trivia" and the game will begin! Alexa will ask you a series of 10 questions, each with four possible answers. With multiple randomized questions, the fun never ends!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, start playing space race trivia
name: Space Race Trivia
shortDescription: Test your knowledge of the space race with Space Race Trivia!
